topics.body:
"@Too_Offensive":/dis/the-time-wasting-thread/post/55269bc46368720db8770100#post_55269bc46368720db8770100
No. My grandma has three dogs. Jack, Samson, and Gertrude. Samson is the youngest and he is TERRIFIED of storms. And last night we had a pretty bad one. Poor dog looked like he was gonna have a panic attack. So I put down my 3DS, go over to the dog bed, and I sat there gently petting his head and talking to him so he would calm down. I did that for about an hour and a half while the storm died out, Next thing I know, I wake up on the dog bed with Samson snuggled up against me.
